org.eclipse.wst.wsdl.binding.soap
Interface SOAPPackage.Literals

Enclosing interface:
SOAPPackage
public static interface SOAPPackage.Literals

Defines literals for the meta objects that represent

  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type
